cross: Cymbidium Hazel Tyers 'Santa Maria' x Cymbidium Satin Dragon 'Cinnabar'

measurements.description: Fourteen flowers on one 72-cm upright inflorescence; sepals and petals off-white, lightly striated longitudinally rose speckles, denser distally; lip white overlaid broad burgundy band distally, burgundy center-stripe band to keels, side lobes 1-cm rose band, keels yellow, lightly spotted burgundy; column white, blushed rose, ventral surface spotted burgundy, anther cap yellow; substance firm; texture matte.
